{"tid":371173,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"9歲譚順生續戰《美國達人秀》 半準決賽慘被評審打槍","createTime":"2017-08-23T13:15:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-24T10:50:30.000Z","uid":23451,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"da2f830b48917ffceb9d1c6c26f7424328261a93","tid":371173,"uid":23451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T13:15:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://ent.ltn.com.tw/m/news/breakingnews/2171929\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fent.ltn.com.tw%2Fm%2Fnews%2Fbreakingnews%2F2171929&d=PIM5DnMyAakKyCDRyl1PyrIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=beb4553b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fent.ltn.com.tw%2Fm%2Fnews%2Fbreakingnews%2F2171929&h=a8a3efd9\" target=\"_blank\">http://ent.ltn.com.tw/m/news/breakingnews/2171929</a><br />\n<br />\n〔娛樂頻道／綜合報導〕有香港小鐵肺之稱的譚芷昀，先前演唱「席琳狄翁」的《My heart will go on》一炮而紅，但今天出戰《美國達人秀》半準決賽時，演唱《When You Believe》，卻慘遭評審打槍，讓她當場面露失落。<br />\n<br />\n9歲的譚芷昀3歲開始學習聲樂，小小年紀便能詮釋多首世界知名名曲，她之所以有這般演唱功力不只是天份，也靠後天學習，今日的《美國達人秀》半準決賽她決定演唱曲風一別以往的《When You Believe》，這首是瑪麗亞凱莉和惠妮休斯頓一同合作的歌曲，演唱完畢卻遭評審「Mel B」批她挑錯歌曲，歌曲難度太高譚芷昀無法詮釋，讓她臉上瞬間失去笑容，但其他評審也趕緊反駁，以她的年紀來說能做到這樣已經很不容易了，更有評審說「妳可以忘記Mel B說的話」指譚芷昀雖然歌唱技巧沒到完美，但天真可愛也是她吸引大眾的原因。"},{"pid":"417fd5ccacd58e067baff7c8b63a564507145daa","tid":371173,"uid":23451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T13:16:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62ddf9f047357312beb42c39c457b2af2f816c20","tid":371173,"uid":46933,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T13:19:06.000Z","msg":"告鳩佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n投訴佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59f9f4e0ab9ee6fe85613e009bfd27883c57b4c5","tid":371173,"uid":45556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T13:19:46.000Z","msg":"topic <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"249b94362eb3e6b04536